        <h1>Privacy Policy for PIN Code Finder</h1>
        <p class="date">Effective Date: April 28, 2025</p>

        <p>At <strong>PIN Code Finder</strong>, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We do not collect any personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, or phone number unless you choose to provide it.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> The app collects device-related data such as your device model, operating system, and other technical data to improve app performance.</li>
            <li><strong>Location Information:</strong> If you allow the app to access your device's location, we may collect your GPS data to provide location-based PIN code searches.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect data on how you interact with the app to improve functionality and user experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide accurate PIN code search results based on your location or manual entry.</li>
            <li>Improve app performance, troubleshoot issues, and enhance the user experience.</li>
            <li>Send occasional updates or support messages related to the app, if you have opted in to notifications.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of data transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>The app may use third-party services that collect information to improve user experience. These services may include analytics tools, advertising networks, or other services.</p>

        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law.</p>

        <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete any personal information you have provided. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us at the email below.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or need assistance with your personal information, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:websynczone@gmail.com">websynczone@gmail.com</a></p>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app and will take effect immediately. Please review this policy regularly to stay informed about how we are protecting your data.</p>

